Dead In The End - Black Eyes demo 2002
Dead In The End - Black Eyes demo 2002

Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on December 20, 2017 Description from Terminal Escape:
A killer four song slab from 2002, just around the time I was phasing out of being a Bay Area resident. Rough around the edges, but with a passion that more than makes up for any technical inadequacies. This was from a time when the lines between raucous basement hardcore and breakneck fastcore and youth crew were kinda blurred...and I (still) contend that this was a good thing.  BLACK EYES
